1
00:01:36,110 --> 00:01:40,990
=Yummy Yummy Yummy=

2
00:01:41,020 --> 00:01:43,940
=Episode 23=

3
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:46,680
♪Better and better♪

4
00:01:46,710 --> 00:01:47,550
Fengxia.

5
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:48,640
Fengxia.

6
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,760
What are you doing?

7
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,780
All the dishes are served.

8
00:01:51,780 --> 00:01:52,990
I have to cook dumplings.

9
00:01:53,300 --> 00:01:54,680
Previously I bought you a carriage.

10
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,480
You didn't like it.

11
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:56,400
You scolded me for it.

12
00:01:56,660 --> 00:01:57,960
Before that, I bought you a ring,

13
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:58,870
but the size was wrong.

14
00:01:58,870 --> 00:01:59,880
You scolded me again.

15
00:02:00,320 --> 00:02:01,160
Today,

16
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:03,350
I bought you another ring
to make up for it.

17
00:02:03,630 --> 00:02:05,600
I hope you can stop scolding me.

18
00:02:09,830 --> 00:02:10,710
Happy Chinese New Year.

19
00:02:29,020 --> 00:02:33,220
(Pavilion of Jade in the Fairy Mountains)

20
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:51,710
Your Highness,

21
00:02:51,710 --> 00:02:52,590
it's getting late.

22
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,040
How about

23
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:55,750
I go back first?

24
00:02:56,270 --> 00:02:57,960
So I won't delay you
entering the palace.

25
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:00,400
Her Highness understands
that you have no time to return home,

26
00:03:00,410 --> 00:03:01,690
and that spending Chinese New Year's Eve

27
00:03:01,690 --> 00:03:03,200
alone away from home must be difficult,

28
00:03:03,220 --> 00:03:04,910
so Her Highness declined
other invitations

29
00:03:04,910 --> 00:03:06,620
and invited you to be here
for a gathering.

30
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:13,140
The news

31
00:03:14,180 --> 00:03:15,670
that I couldn't afford the travel fare

32
00:03:15,670 --> 00:03:16,220
to return home

33
00:03:16,620 --> 00:03:18,540
has somehow reached you.

34
00:03:18,820 --> 00:03:20,420
I just feel

35
00:03:20,420 --> 00:03:22,260
that entering the palace
is even more boring.

36
00:03:22,860 --> 00:03:24,260
It's better to stay here

37
00:03:25,420 --> 00:03:28,540
and enjoy tea and chess
with a close friend.

38
00:03:30,250 --> 00:03:32,220
There are even night outings
during the festival.

39
00:03:32,220 --> 00:03:34,620
I haven't been to a lantern festival
in many years.

40
00:03:35,790 --> 00:03:38,420
How about you come along

41
00:03:38,620 --> 00:03:39,460
with me?

42
00:03:47,460 --> 00:03:48,300
It's a copper coin.

43
00:03:49,260 --> 00:03:50,220
Impressive.

44
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,980
- You got it.
- I got a copper coin.

45
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:54,340
Does eating a copper coin

46
00:03:54,340 --> 00:03:55,340
mean

47
00:03:55,340 --> 00:03:56,300
that in the Chinese New Year

48
00:03:56,300 --> 00:03:57,780
I can have whatever I want?

49
00:03:57,780 --> 00:03:58,620
Yes.

50
00:03:59,140 --> 00:04:00,660
So what do you want for the Chinese New Year?

51
00:04:04,460 --> 00:04:05,420
Grandpa,

52
00:04:05,420 --> 00:04:06,420
wishing you prosperity.

53
00:04:06,420 --> 00:04:07,500
Give me money.

54
00:04:08,410 --> 00:04:09,300
Good girl.

55
00:04:09,300 --> 00:04:10,140
Sure.

56
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:12,500
I've already prepared it for you.

57
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:13,350
Here, take it.

58
00:04:13,350 --> 00:04:14,260
Thank you, grandpa.

59
00:04:14,940 --> 00:04:16,380
Grandma, wishing you prosperity.

60
00:04:16,380 --> 00:04:17,340
Give me money.

61
00:04:18,180 --> 00:04:20,140
I forgot today. What should I do?

62
00:04:23,660 --> 00:04:24,500
She feels wronged.

63
00:04:27,550 --> 00:04:29,180
I've already prepared it
for a long time.

64
00:04:29,180 --> 00:04:30,020
Thank you, grandma.

65
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,100
You're welcome.

66
00:04:33,700 --> 00:04:35,340
Happy Chinese New Year, Auntie.

67
00:04:37,380 --> 00:04:39,060
Happy Chinese New Year, Yangyang.

68
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:41,180
Thank you, Auntie.

69
00:04:41,860 --> 00:04:42,700
Deyuan.

70
00:04:42,700 --> 00:04:43,820
Happy Chinese New Year.

71
00:04:44,060 --> 00:04:44,900
It's mine?

72
00:04:44,900 --> 00:04:45,780
Of course.

73
00:04:45,780 --> 00:04:47,460
You're also part of our family.

74
00:04:47,860 --> 00:04:49,060
Thank you, milady.

75
00:04:49,620 --> 00:04:51,060
Ming, look.

76
00:04:53,100 --> 00:04:53,980
Mr. Lin.

77
00:04:53,980 --> 00:04:54,940
Happy Chinese New Year.

78
00:04:56,220 --> 00:04:57,580
I'm really not prepared.

79
00:05:02,940 --> 00:05:03,780
Take it all.

80
00:05:05,580 --> 00:05:06,500
That's a lot.

81
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:08,580
Mr. Lin, this is way too much.

82
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:10,740
Including the share for me
and Liu Chang.

83
00:05:11,420 --> 00:05:12,260
It's not much.

84
00:05:12,460 --> 00:05:13,420
Here, take it.

85
00:05:13,420 --> 00:05:15,740
Yangyang, you should give Mr. Lin
a kowtow for this.

86
00:05:16,620 --> 00:05:17,460
Thank you, Mr. Lin.

87
00:05:19,140 --> 00:05:20,420
May everything go smoothly.

88
00:05:20,420 --> 00:05:21,610
- This kid.
- Go ahead.

89
00:05:22,980 --> 00:05:23,820
Yangyang.

90
00:05:24,620 --> 00:05:25,740
Look, what is this?

91
00:05:26,740 --> 00:05:27,580
This is...

92
00:05:30,980 --> 00:05:32,780
This is the lucky money from my father.

93
00:05:33,220 --> 00:05:34,540
My father even sent a letter.

94
00:05:34,540 --> 00:05:35,570
Here, take it.

95
00:05:36,820 --> 00:05:38,060
Let's open it and read.

96
00:05:38,420 --> 00:05:39,900
This is written by Gongcai.

97
00:05:40,900 --> 00:05:42,100
Let me see.

98
00:05:42,100 --> 00:05:42,940
Here.

99
00:05:44,850 --> 00:05:46,180
This is really written by Gongcai.

100
00:05:46,180 --> 00:05:47,460
Let me read it to everyone.

101
00:05:49,180 --> 00:05:50,020
Family members,

102
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:52,220
when you read this letter,

103
00:05:52,220 --> 00:05:53,500
I am already on my way

104
00:05:53,500 --> 00:05:54,820
to the peak.

105
00:05:55,340 --> 00:05:56,340
Don't worry.

106
00:05:56,340 --> 00:05:57,860
With my personal charm,

107
00:05:57,860 --> 00:05:58,740
wherever I am,

108
00:05:59,140 --> 00:06:01,020
I will be warmly sought after.

109
00:06:02,380 --> 00:06:03,220
Ladies and gentlemen,

110
00:06:03,940 --> 00:06:05,640
this kind of talk show

111
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:07,500
is probably something
you haven't heard before.

112
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:08,900
You shamelessly dragged us here.

113
00:06:08,900 --> 00:06:10,280
Didn't you say you don't want money

114
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:11,540
and you provide tea and snacks?

115
00:06:11,860 --> 00:06:13,540
Where is the stuff? Where is it?

116
00:06:13,740 --> 00:06:15,180
Where is the stuff you promised?

117
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:16,740
Everyone, calm down.

118
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:17,900
I'll definitely provide.

119
00:06:17,900 --> 00:06:19,180
But if

120
00:06:19,180 --> 00:06:20,580
you think I speak quite well,

121
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:22,300
I still hope everyone can offer me

122
00:06:22,300 --> 00:06:23,180
a couple of coins.

123
00:06:23,540 --> 00:06:24,420
That's him.

124
00:06:24,740 --> 00:06:26,380
I saw him nearby yesterday.

125
00:06:26,380 --> 00:06:28,020
He talked about gender equality;

126
00:06:28,020 --> 00:06:29,880
ladies should be independent
and self-reliant.

127
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:31,580
He even asked my wife divorce me.

128
00:06:32,060 --> 00:06:33,370
He mislead the public.

129
00:06:33,370 --> 00:06:34,210
- I didn't.
- Is that so?

130
00:06:34,210 --> 00:06:35,740
- Hit him.
- Beat him to death.

131
00:06:38,090 --> 00:06:38,940
Hit him.

132
00:06:39,030 --> 00:06:40,020
Don't run.

133
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:42,730
Stop!

134
00:06:44,620 --> 00:06:45,520
Stop!

135
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:46,430
Don't run.

136
00:06:47,140 --> 00:06:48,340
I'm all good.

137
00:06:48,340 --> 00:06:49,620
I just miss Yangyang.

138
00:06:50,060 --> 00:06:50,900
Yangyang,

139
00:06:51,100 --> 00:06:52,860
you are the daughter
I am most proud of.

140
00:06:53,340 --> 00:06:55,140
In the future you must be like me...

141
00:06:56,500 --> 00:06:57,700
- Become...
- Perform or not?

142
00:06:57,700 --> 00:06:58,820
- Think much.
- Very soon.

143
00:06:58,820 --> 00:06:59,660
Be enterprising.

144
00:06:59,820 --> 00:07:01,020
Innovative.

145
00:07:01,580 --> 00:07:02,980
I once had a large number of fans

146
00:07:02,980 --> 00:07:04,460
in Yong'an,

147
00:07:04,620 --> 00:07:06,380
and achieved some small successes.

148
00:07:06,700 --> 00:07:08,460
But I never became complacent
about it;

149
00:07:08,460 --> 00:07:09,660
instead, I keep seeking

150
00:07:09,660 --> 00:07:11,100
new entrepreneurial directions.

151
00:07:11,860 --> 00:07:13,020
Life is just like this,

152
00:07:13,020 --> 00:07:14,300
full of possibilities.

153
00:07:14,860 --> 00:07:16,020
Yangyang,

154
00:07:16,020 --> 00:07:16,940
you know what?

155
00:07:17,300 --> 00:07:18,980
My current job is very good.

156
00:07:19,340 --> 00:07:20,460
High income,

157
00:07:20,940 --> 00:07:21,860
decent,

158
00:07:22,380 --> 00:07:23,220
stable.

159
00:07:23,420 --> 00:07:24,900
When dealing with colleagues at work,

160
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:25,900
I have always approached

161
00:07:25,910 --> 00:07:27,960
with an attitude of cooperation
and mutual benefit.

162
00:07:28,260 --> 00:07:29,220
So,

163
00:07:29,350 --> 00:07:30,220
I can easily

164
00:07:30,220 --> 00:07:32,180
get along with everyone.

165
00:07:32,540 --> 00:07:34,580
You don't need to worry about me.

166
00:07:43,390 --> 00:07:45,780
Awesome!

167
00:07:49,300 --> 00:07:50,500
Are you going to fight or not?

168
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:51,580
- Hurry up.
- Exactly.

169
00:07:51,580 --> 00:07:52,540
Do it quickly.

170
00:07:52,540 --> 00:07:53,420
Do it!

171
00:07:53,420 --> 00:07:54,660
Don't just stand there watching.

172
00:07:54,820 --> 00:07:55,860
Hit him.

173
00:07:58,180 --> 00:07:59,020
Do it.

174
00:08:05,740 --> 00:08:06,860
Didn't you eat?

175
00:08:07,460 --> 00:08:08,300
Didn't you eat?

176
00:08:08,660 --> 00:08:09,500
OK.

177
00:08:10,060 --> 00:08:10,900
I'm telling you,

178
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:12,500
you can hit me anywhere you want,

179
00:08:12,740 --> 00:08:13,940
just not the face.

180
00:08:14,540 --> 00:08:16,020
Otherwise my female fans

181
00:08:16,700 --> 00:08:17,900
will be unhappy.

182
00:08:32,260 --> 00:08:35,180
Awesome!

183
00:08:57,340 --> 00:08:58,420
It's almost Chinese New Year.

184
00:08:58,700 --> 00:09:00,740
Wish my family a Happy Chinese New Year.

185
00:09:01,140 --> 00:09:02,580
If there are any other developments,

186
00:09:03,100 --> 00:09:04,900
I will write again to inform you.

187
00:09:05,460 --> 00:09:06,620
May you all be safe and sound.

188
00:09:07,660 --> 00:09:08,500
Do not miss me.

189
00:09:09,420 --> 00:09:10,260
Applause.

190
00:09:11,100 --> 00:09:12,700
- Give him applause.
- Great.

191
00:09:12,700 --> 00:09:14,500
Gongcai has finally grown.

192
00:09:16,100 --> 00:09:16,940
Don't cry, don't cry.

193
00:09:16,940 --> 00:09:18,740
Yangyang, you should be happy.

194
00:09:18,740 --> 00:09:19,580
Isn't it?

195
00:09:20,260 --> 00:09:21,180
Come on.

196
00:09:21,180 --> 00:09:22,220
Let's keep eating.

197
00:09:22,860 --> 00:09:23,700
Let me tell you all.

198
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,900
There are quite a few good omens
in these dumplings.

199
00:09:25,900 --> 00:09:27,540
Let's see what each of you can get.

200
00:09:28,660 --> 00:09:29,990
Come on, start eating.

201
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:30,900
Alright, let's eat.

202
00:09:30,900 --> 00:09:31,740
OK.

203
00:09:32,020 --> 00:09:33,340
Come on, Mr. Lin.

204
00:09:33,700 --> 00:09:34,860
Try this filling.

205
00:09:35,500 --> 00:09:36,380
Thank you.

206
00:09:36,380 --> 00:09:37,220
You're welcome.

207
00:09:38,300 --> 00:09:40,440
By the way, there's one more thing
I want to announce.

208
00:09:41,300 --> 00:09:42,460
Our restaurant's renovation

209
00:09:42,460 --> 00:09:43,940
will be finished soon.

210
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:45,820
It will be ready to open
after the Chinese New Year.

211
00:09:45,820 --> 00:09:47,700
- Great.
- Great.

212
00:09:50,180 --> 00:09:51,820
Come on, everyone, eat up.

213
00:09:52,020 --> 00:09:52,860
Let's eat.

214
00:09:53,380 --> 00:09:54,220
Let's eat.

215
00:10:02,660 --> 00:10:03,740
Auspicious Chinese New Year.

216
00:10:05,700 --> 00:10:06,540
Happy Chinese New Year.

217
00:10:20,260 --> 00:10:22,740
(Miss You in Yong'an)
The Princess has arrived.

218
00:10:26,220 --> 00:10:27,540
Greetings, Your Highness.

219
00:10:28,660 --> 00:10:29,660
Today is Chinese New Year's Eve.

220
00:10:29,660 --> 00:10:31,520
No need to be constrained
by these formalities.

221
00:10:32,340 --> 00:10:34,140
Are you about to go out?

222
00:10:35,220 --> 00:10:36,460
Censor Pei and I

223
00:10:37,420 --> 00:10:38,900
just finished admiring the lanterns.

224
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:41,740
I was thinking of coming to your place
for some hotpot.

225
00:10:42,180 --> 00:10:44,220
Looks like this is bad timing, huh?

226
00:10:44,740 --> 00:10:47,060
No, Yangyang wants
to go see the lanterns.

227
00:10:47,060 --> 00:10:47,940
My father and mother

228
00:10:47,940 --> 00:10:49,120
have already taken them there.

229
00:10:49,300 --> 00:10:51,460
I'm not interested in those things.

230
00:10:51,460 --> 00:10:52,300
It's alright.

231
00:10:52,580 --> 00:10:53,420
Deyuan.

232
00:10:53,460 --> 00:10:55,480
You've been talking
about Aoshan Lanterns all day.

233
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:56,580
You catch up with them.

234
00:10:58,020 --> 00:10:59,290
Deyuan, go ahead.

235
00:10:59,780 --> 00:11:01,220
I will stay with your lady.

236
00:11:01,740 --> 00:11:02,900
Liu Chang is here too.

237
00:11:02,900 --> 00:11:03,740
It's OK.

238
00:11:10,940 --> 00:11:11,860
Your Highness,

239
00:11:11,860 --> 00:11:12,780
please take a seat.

240
00:11:14,580 --> 00:11:15,420
Please.

241
00:11:24,620 --> 00:11:26,020
The newly heated Tusu wine.

242
00:11:26,020 --> 00:11:27,660
Drink some first to warm up.

243
00:11:30,260 --> 00:11:31,220
Lady Shen,

244
00:11:31,580 --> 00:11:34,060
the tofu from your restaurant
is quite peculiar.

245
00:11:34,380 --> 00:11:35,580
I have never seen it before.

246
00:11:35,580 --> 00:11:38,020
Why are there so many holes?

247
00:11:38,220 --> 00:11:40,140
Cut the tofu into square cubes,

248
00:11:40,140 --> 00:11:41,340
and blanch with salt,

249
00:11:41,340 --> 00:11:42,820
then holes will form and expand.

250
00:11:42,920 --> 00:11:44,730
After placing it in the ice cellar
to freeze,

251
00:11:44,740 --> 00:11:45,550
it will be like this.

252
00:11:45,660 --> 00:11:46,780
Put it into the soup.

253
00:11:46,780 --> 00:11:48,100
It will be especially flavorful.

254
00:11:51,620 --> 00:11:52,660
Truly delicious.

255
00:11:53,820 --> 00:11:54,660
Delicious.

256
00:11:54,660 --> 00:11:56,220
I'm glad you like it.

257
00:11:57,220 --> 00:11:58,060
Lady Shen,

258
00:11:58,580 --> 00:11:59,980
today, regardless of status,

259
00:11:59,980 --> 00:12:01,340
why not sit down with us?

260
00:12:01,340 --> 00:12:02,780
Let's drink and sing together,

261
00:12:02,940 --> 00:12:04,420
and have a lively time.

262
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:10,380
Then thank you, Your Highness.

263
00:12:20,620 --> 00:12:21,460
Here.

264
00:12:22,820 --> 00:12:26,540
Auspicious Chinese New Year.

265
00:12:32,060 --> 00:12:32,900
Mr. Lin,

266
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,220
your alcohol tolerance is poor.

267
00:12:34,220 --> 00:12:35,580
Better drink a little less.

268
00:12:37,090 --> 00:12:37,940
OK.

269
00:12:37,940 --> 00:12:38,780
Lady Shen,

270
00:12:39,140 --> 00:12:40,460
you said Anran

271
00:12:40,460 --> 00:12:41,550
has poor alcohol tolerance?

272
00:12:42,820 --> 00:12:43,820
His alcohol tolerance...

273
00:12:44,740 --> 00:12:45,580
Anran,

274
00:12:45,820 --> 00:12:47,140
could it be

275
00:12:47,140 --> 00:12:49,300
that you lied to Lady Shen?

276
00:12:49,820 --> 00:12:50,740
Twelfth Master,

277
00:12:50,740 --> 00:12:52,160
what nonsense are you talking about?

278
00:12:52,460 --> 00:12:53,580
Is it nonsense?

279
00:12:53,900 --> 00:12:54,820
I did hear

280
00:12:54,820 --> 00:12:57,380
you can hold your liquor
without getting drunk.

281
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:58,730
That time, Second Master Huan

282
00:12:58,750 --> 00:13:00,660
somehow offended you.

283
00:13:00,770 --> 00:13:02,500
His uncle hosted a banquet
and invited you.

284
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:03,580
He said

285
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:05,940
you drank all of their Jiannan Wine,

286
00:13:06,180 --> 00:13:07,700
still without changing your expression.

287
00:13:10,260 --> 00:13:11,860
It's all old news.

288
00:13:11,860 --> 00:13:13,180
