00:31:00,440 --> 00:31:03,100
Happy Chinese New Year.

571
00:31:03,380 --> 00:31:05,500
Your place is really quite unique.

572
00:31:05,500 --> 00:31:07,240
- The kids are willing to play here.
- Yeah.

573
00:31:07,500 --> 00:31:09,020
As long as they like it.

574
00:31:09,340 --> 00:31:10,300
Children,

575
00:31:10,300 --> 00:31:11,460
want to drink soy milk?

576
00:31:11,490 --> 00:31:12,730
- Auntie.
- I want to drink.

577
00:31:12,730 --> 00:31:14,140
I want to drink.

578
00:31:14,140 --> 00:31:15,140
Yangyang.

579
00:31:15,420 --> 00:31:17,020
I want to drink.

580
00:31:18,280 --> 00:31:19,340
- Line up.
- Be careful.

581
00:31:20,540 --> 00:31:21,380
Look.

582
00:31:22,980 --> 00:31:24,340
These naughty kids

583
00:31:24,340 --> 00:31:26,100
only listen to Yangyang.

584
00:31:26,100 --> 00:31:27,010
Yes.

585
00:31:27,010 --> 00:31:28,380
Come here, children.

586
00:31:28,580 --> 00:31:29,660
Be careful, it's hot.

587
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:30,860
- Auntie.
- Good girl.

588
00:31:30,860 --> 00:31:32,690
After hearing that I study
in Hongwen Academy,

589
00:31:32,690 --> 00:31:33,860
they all admire me.

590
00:31:34,140 --> 00:31:36,180
Then should you be a good role model

591
00:31:36,180 --> 00:31:37,780
and lead them?

592
00:31:38,860 --> 00:31:41,020
The mentor said
you are a promising talent.

593
00:31:41,020 --> 00:31:42,240
If you can take the right path,

594
00:31:42,240 --> 00:31:43,480
you will achieve great things.

595
00:31:43,750 --> 00:31:44,940
Then next spring,

596
00:31:44,940 --> 00:31:46,020
are you...

