606
00:31:59,380 --> 00:32:00,740
all matters
concerning the common people

607
00:32:00,740 --> 00:32:02,260
- must be resolved in seven days.
- Be careful. So hot.

608
00:32:02,260 --> 00:32:03,350
- In case of dereliction of duty,
- Thank you.

609
00:32:03,360 --> 00:32:04,700
then the people may go beat the drum

610
00:32:04,700 --> 00:32:05,910
to report it to the Prefecture.

611
00:32:05,980 --> 00:32:07,080
This matter in my family

612
00:32:07,080 --> 00:32:08,460
has been delayed for several years.

613
00:32:08,470 --> 00:32:10,180
They all pass the buck to each other.

614
00:32:10,730 --> 00:32:12,220
If it weren't for the decisive actions

615
00:32:12,220 --> 00:32:13,180
of Mr. Lin,

616
00:32:13,340 --> 00:32:14,900
