617
00:32:15,420 --> 00:32:17,500
No wonder everyone praises him.

618
00:32:17,700 --> 00:32:18,940
A rare and admirable official.

619
00:32:18,940 --> 00:32:20,220
Exactly. With him here,

620
00:32:20,220 --> 00:32:21,580
