622
00:32:32,690 --> 00:32:33,660
- Wait a minute.
- Here.

623
00:32:33,660 --> 00:32:34,700
Mr. Lin will be out soon.

624
00:32:34,940 --> 00:32:36,100
Add some hot water.

625
00:32:37,050 --> 00:32:38,130
- Be careful.
- Thank you.

626
00:32:40,540 --> 00:32:42,060
The Lantern Festival isn't over yet.

627
00:32:42,060 --> 00:32:43,420
Mr. Lin has already dragged me out.

628
00:32:43,980 --> 00:32:44,900
Stop complaining.

629
00:32:45,140 --> 00:32:46,020
I'm telling you,

630
00:32:46,420 --> 00:32:47,860
although I can't read a single word,

631
00:32:47,860 --> 00:32:48,900
I remember clearly

632
00:32:48,900 --> 00:32:50,340
every single word spoken by Mr. Lin.

633
00:32:50,340 --> 00:32:52,100
Matters of the people,
whether big or small,

634
00:32:52,100 --> 00:32:52,990
all should be reported.

635
00:32:52,990 --> 00:32:53,800
Whatever is reported,

636
00:32:53,800 --> 00:32:54,620
it must be resolved.

637
00:32:54,620 --> 00:32:55,460
Look.

638
00:32:55,640 --> 00:32:57,140
All the people of Yong'an praise him.

639
00:32:57,140 --> 00:32:58,990
Even His Majesty speak words
of gold and jade,

640
00:32:59,190 --> 00:33:02,140
praising Mr. Lin as the Zhao Guanghan
of our dynasty.

641
00:33:02,230 --> 00:33:03,110
Think about it.

642
00:33:03,120 --> 00:33:04,500
Since even His Majesty has said so,

643
00:33:04,570 --> 00:33:05,420
from now on,

644
00:33:05,420 --> 00:33:06,900
if anything happens in the Prefecture,

645
00:33:06,900 --> 00:33:08,100
it will be much easier for us

646
00:33:08,200 --> 00:33:09,670
to ask various departments for help.

647
00:33:10,380 --> 00:33:11,980
Well, that's true.

648
00:33:12,570 --> 00:33:14,220
But he hasn't been home

649
00:33:14,330 --> 00:33:15,620
these past few days either,

650
00:33:16,110 --> 00:33:18,000
getting up earlier than the roosters
every day.

651
00:33:18,000 --> 00:33:19,040
It seems to me like

652
00:33:19,050 --> 00:33:21,040
when Wang Laosan divorced his wife,

653
00:33:21,140 --> 00:33:23,120
he could only immerse himself
in official duties.

654
00:33:23,480 --> 00:33:24,350
Don't worry.

655
00:33:24,360 --> 00:33:26,100
Even if it's the Wei family
from Guanzhong,

656
00:33:26,140 --> 00:33:27,860
the Prefecture will never harbor them.

657
00:33:27,880 --> 00:33:28,840
Your farmland

658
00:33:28,900 --> 00:33:29,880
will surely be recovered.

659
00:33:31,180 --> 00:33:33,380
- Thank you, Mr. Lin.
- My pleasure.

660
00:33:33,380 --> 00:33:34,260
Don't talk nonsense.

661
00:33:35,340 --> 00:33:36,420
Indeed.

662
00:33:36,420 --> 00:33:39,300
I haven't seen Mr. Lin's cousin
for a long time.

663
00:33:39,300 --> 00:33:40,200
I'm telling you,

664
00:33:40,200 --> 00:33:41,440
these past few days, Mr. Lin...

665
00:33:42,580 --> 00:33:43,420
Could it be

666
00:33:43,860 --> 00:33:44,740
that...

667
00:33:46,180 --> 00:33:47,380
- Mr. Lin.
- Mr. Lin.

668
00:33:48,220 --> 00:33:49,460
Criticizing your superiors,

669
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:51,360
what crime should you be charged?

670
00:33:51,420 --> 00:33:52,260
We should be...

671
00:33:52,420 --> 00:33:54,100
Just punish him.

672
00:33:54,100 --> 00:33:55,950
As long as you don't dock my salary,
it's fine.

673
00:33:56,380 --> 00:33:58,540
Mr. Lin, it wasn't me who said that.

674
00:33:58,540 --> 00:33:59,380
Alright.

675
00:33:59,900 --> 00:34:00,820
I'll punish you

676
00:34:02,780 --> 00:34:03,820
