forcibly occupying land.

680
00:34:08,740 --> 00:34:09,620
Really?

681
00:34:09,900 --> 00:34:10,740
Hurry up and go.

682
00:34:11,820 --> 00:34:12,860
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

683
