751
00:38:04,940 --> 00:38:06,300
and also need to vent.

752
00:38:07,180 --> 00:38:09,060
But there are many ways to vent.

753
00:38:10,020 --> 00:38:11,540
I don't want you to hurt yourself.

754
00:38:11,540 --> 00:38:12,380
Do you know?

755
00:38:12,580 --> 00:38:14,180
I didn't mean it.

756
00:38:15,740 --> 00:38:18,500
I just thought
of the desensitization method.

757
00:38:19,100 --> 00:38:20,460
When I couldn't let go,

758
00:38:20,460 --> 00:38:22,060
I would just tighten the rope.

759
00:38:22,060 --> 00:38:23,340
People are afraid of pain.

760
00:38:23,340 --> 00:38:25,340
If it hurts, I won't think anymore.

761
00:38:25,340 --> 00:38:26,500
I'm in pain.

762
00:38:26,500 --> 00:38:28,540
I have no backbone.
I still keep thinking about it.

763
00:38:29,820 --> 00:38:31,140
My silly girl.

764
00:38:32,060 --> 00:38:33,220
My silly girl.

765
00:38:35,980 --> 00:38:38,140
Who said you have no backbone?

766
00:38:39,220 --> 00:38:41,100
You like someone so sincerely.

767
00:38:41,100 --> 00:38:42,460
So courageous!

768
00:38:46,100 --> 00:38:47,380
It's a pity.

769
00:38:49,340 --> 00:38:50,660
You have no way.

770
00:38:55,860 --> 00:38:56,740
But you know what,

771
00:38:56,740 --> 00:38:57,580
Jicai?

772
00:38:57,980 --> 00:38:59,740
You are bravely cutting your losses.

773
00:39:00,180 --> 00:39:01,620
You've already done really well.

774
00:39:01,620 --> 00:39:03,380
I'm useless.

775
00:39:04,700 --> 00:39:05,940
Don't cry, don't cry.

776
00:39:05,940 --> 00:39:06,780
Don't cry anymore.

777
00:39:07,120 --> 00:39:08,580
Don't hurt yourself again next time.

778
00:39:08,580 --> 00:39:09,660
Do you know?

779
00:39:15,140 --> 00:39:15,980
Here.

780
00:39:21,820 --> 00:39:23,700
Don't cry, it's OK.

781
00:39:23,860 --> 00:39:25,220
I'm here.

782
00:39:27,180 --> 00:39:29,140
Your crying sounds like water boiling.

783
00:39:29,140 --> 00:39:30,420
Who did you take after?

